Tier System
Tier 1 — CONFIRMED
Tier 2 — WIKI
Tier 3 — THEORY
8) SCRIPT REQUIREMENTS
Write a TikTok script with these rules:

Style
conversational
enthusiastic
slightly dramatic
Include:

1 personal reaction
1 surprising fact
1 light humor moment
Hook Rule
The first line must be a curiosity hook.

Script Rules
90 to 100 words
simple English, B1 level
focus on one micro-detail only
end with another curiosity hook or open loop
Number Rule
Write all numbers as words.

9) VISUAL STRATEGY
Use only dynamic scenes for clip suggestions.

10) YOUTUBE SEARCH QUERIES
Provide 3 YouTube queries.

Each must include:

